Only the Prince's Blade can control
Genbu's course and bearing.

rows.label: tlk44510181_03_msg0002

It was meant to stay submerged for
as long as was safe, but...

rows.label: tlk44510181_03_msg0003

happened to the Sanctus Chain...

We shouldn't be here dithering while
the evacuation is underway.
